# Large Codebase Navigation

Skill for efficiently exploring and understanding large codebases, finding functions, tracing dependencies, and understanding system architecture.

## When to Use

Use this skill when:
- Starting work on unfamiliar code
- Finding where a feature is implemented
- Understanding code dependencies
- Mapping out system architecture
- Locating related functions
- Tracing execution flow

## Navigation Strategy

### Phase 1: Orient

```blitzbasic
; First steps when entering a new codebase
Function Orient_Codebase()
    ; 1. Find main entry point
    Print "Main files:"
    LocateFile("main.bb")
    LocateFile("Main.bb")
    LocateFile("main.c")
    LocateFile("index.js")

    ; 2. Find configuration
    Print "Config files:"
    LocateFile("package.json")
    LocateFile("README*")
    LocateFile("AGENTS.md")

    ; 3. Find directory structure
    ListTopLevelDirectories()

    ; 4. Identify file count and types
    CountFilesByExtension()
End Function
```

### Phase 2: Map

```blitzbasic
; Build mental map of codebase
Function Map_Codebase()
    ; Group files by purpose
    CreateFileGroup("Core", "*Main*, *Init*, *Game*")
    CreateFileGroup("NPCs", "*NPC*, *Entity*, *AI*")
    CreateFileGroup("Graphics", "*Render*, *Draw*, *Mesh*")
    CreateFileGroup("Audio", "*Sound*, *Music*, *FMod*")
    CreateFileGroup("UI", "*Menu*, *HUD*, *Interface*")
    CreateFileGroup("System", "*Save*, *Load*, *File*")

    ; Identify largest files (most complex)
    GetLargestFiles(10)

    ; Identify most frequently referenced files
    GetMostReferencedFiles(10)
End Function
```

### Phase 3: Drill Down

```blitzbasic
; Focus on specific area
Function Drill_Down(target$)
    Select target$
        Case "NPCs"
            Drill_NPCs()
        Case "SaveSystem"
            Drill_SaveLoad()
        Case "GameLoop"
            Drill_GameLoop()
        Default
            Drill_Custom(target$)
    End Select
End Function
```

## Finding Functions

### By Name

```blitzbasic
; Find function definitions
Function Find_Function(name$)
    results$ = Grep("Function " + name$, "*.bb")
    Print results$
    Return results
End Function

; Find all functions in file
Function List_Functions(file$)
    lines$ = Grep("^Function ", file$)
    ForEach line$ in lines$
        Print ExtractFunctionName(line$)
    Next
End Function

; Find function calls
Function Find_Calls(functionName$)
    results$ = Grep(functionName$, "*.bb")
    Print results$
    Return results
End Function
```

### By Pattern

```blitzbasic
; Find all NPC-related functions
Function Find_NPC_Functions()
    Print "NPC Creation:"
    Grep("Function CreateNPC", "*.bb")

    Print "NPC Updates:"
    Grep("Function UpdateNPC", "*.bb")

    Print "NPC State Management:"
    Grep("Function.*NPC.*State", "*.bb")
End Function

; Find all save/load functions
Function Find_SaveLoad_Functions()
    Grep("Function Save", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function Load", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function Write", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function Read", "*.bb")
End Function

; Find all event handlers
Function Find_EventHandlers()
    Grep("Function.*Event", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function.*On.*Event", "*.bb")
End Function
```

## Tracing Dependencies

### Function Dependencies

```blitzbasic
; Find what a function calls
Function Trace_Calls(functionName$)
    Print "Functions called by " + functionName$ + ":"
    calls$ = Grep(functionName$ + "\(", "*.bb")

    ; Filter to function calls
    ForEach call$ in calls$
        If IsFunctionCall(call$)
            Print "  " + ExtractFunctionName(call$)
        End If
    Next
End Function

; Find what calls a function
Function Trace_CalledBy(functionName$)
    Print "Functions that call " + functionName$ + ":"
    callers$ = Grep(functionName$, "*.bb")

    ; Filter to call sites
    ForEach line$ in callers$
        If IsFunctionCall(line$)
            Print "  " + GetCurrentFunction(line$)
        End If
    Next
End Function
```

### Variable Dependencies

```blitzbasic
; Find where variable is used
Function Find_VariableUsage(variableName$)
    Print "Variable " + variableName$ + " used in:"
    Grep(variableName$, "*.bb")
End Function

; Find where variable is set
Function Find_VariableSets(variableName$)
    Print "Variable " + variableName$ + " set in:"
    Grep(variableName$ + " =", "*.bb")
    Grep(variableName$ + =, "*.bb")  ; With space
End Function

; Find global variables
Function Find_GlobalVariables()
    Grep("^Global ", "*.bb")
End Function
```

### File Dependencies

```blitzbasic
; Find file includes
Function Find_Includes(file$)
    Grep("#Include", file$)
End Function

; Find files that include target
Function Find_IncludedBy(targetFile$)
    Grep(targetFile$, "*.bb")
End Function
```

## Understanding Systems

### NPC System Overview

```blitzbasic
Function Understand_NPCSystem()
    Print "=== NPC System Overview ==="

    ; Find NPC type definitions
    Print "Type definitions:"
    Grep("Type NPCs", "*.bb")

    ; Find NPC creation
    Print "Creation functions:"
    Grep("Function CreateNPC", "*.bb")

    ; Find main update loop
    Print "Main update:"
    Grep("Function UpdateNPCs", "*.bb")

    ; Find state machine
    Print "State definitions:"
    Grep("Const STATE_", "*.bb")

    ; Find behavior functions
    Print "Behavior functions:"
    Grep("Function UpdateSCP", "*.bb")

    ; Find NPC initialization
    Print "Initialization:"
    Grep("Function InitNPCs", "*.bb")

    Print "=== End Overview ==="
End Function
```

### Save System Overview

```blitzbasic
Function Understand_SaveSystem()
    Print "=== Save System Overview ==="

    ; Find save function
    Print "Main save:"
    Grep("Function SaveGame", "*.bb")

    ; Find load function
    Print "Main load:"
    Grep("Function LoadGame", "*.bb")

    ; Find what gets saved
    Print "Data saved:"
    Grep("Function.*Save.*Data", "*.bb")
    Grep("WriteInt.*Player", "*.bb")
    Grep("WriteString.*Player", "*.bb")

    ; Find format info
    Print "File format:"
    Grep("Function WriteFile", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function ReadFile", "*.bb")

    ; Find save slots
    Print "Save slots:"
    Grep("Const.*SAVE.*SLOT", "*.bb")
End Function
```

### Game Loop Overview

```blitzbasic
Function Understand_GameLoop()
    Print "=== Game Loop Overview ==="

    ; Find main entry
    Print "Main entry:"
    LocateFile("main.bb")
    LocateFile("Main.bb")

    ; Find loop
    Print "Game loop:"
    Grep("While.*Not.*AppTerminate", "*.bb")
    Grep("While.*True", "*.bb")

    ; Find phases
    Print "Update phase:"
    Grep("Function Update", "*.bb")

    Print "Render phase:"
    Grep("Function Render", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function Draw", "*.bb")

    ; Find input handling
    Print "Input:"
    Grep("Function HandleInput", "*.bb")
    Grep("Function UpdateInput", "*.bb")
End Function
```

## File Summarization

### Summarize File

```blitzbasic
Function Summarize_File(file$)
    Print "=== " + file$ + " ==="

    ; Count lines
    lineCount = CountLines(file$)
    Print "Lines: " + lineCount

    ; List functions
    functions$ = Grep("^Function ", file$)
    Print "Functions (" + CountItems(functions$) + "):"
    ForEach func$ in functions$
        Print "  - " + ExtractFunctionName(func$)
    Next

    ; List types
    types$ = Grep("^Type ", file$)
    Print "Types (" + CountItems(types$) + "):"
    ForEach type$ in types$
        Print "  - " + ExtractTypeName(type$)
    Next

    ; List globals
    globals$ = Grep("^Global ", file$)
    Print "Globals (" + CountItems(globals$) + "):"
    ForEach global$ in globals$
        Print "  - " + ExtractGlobalName(global$)
    Next

    ; Find includes
    includes$ = Grep("#Include", file$)
    Print "Includes (" + CountItems(includes$) + "):"
    ForEach inc$ in includes$
        Print "  - " + ExtractIncludePath(inc$)
    Next

    ; Find constants
    constants$ = Grep("^Const ", file$)
    Print "Constants (" + CountItems(constants$) + "):"
End Function
```

### Compare

```blitz Filesbasic
Function Compare_Files(file1$, file2$)
    ; Compare sizes
    size1 = FileSize(file1$)
    size2 = FileSize(file2$)
    Print file1$ + ": " + size1 + " bytes"
    Print file2$ + ": " + size2 + " bytes"

    ; Compare function counts
    funcs1 = CountFunctions(file1$)
    funcs2 = CountFunctions(file2$)
    Print "Functions: " + funcs1 + " vs " + funcs2

    ; Find common functions
    common$ = IntersectFunctionLists(file1$, file2$)
    Print "Common functions: " + CountItems(common$)

    ; Find unique functions
    unique1$ = SubtractFunctionLists(file1$, file2$)
    unique2$ = SubtractFunctionLists(file2$, file1$)
    Print "Unique to " + file1$ + ": " + CountItems(unique1$)
    Print "Unique to " + file2$ + ": " + CountItems(unique2$)
End Function
```

## Code Patterns

### State Machine Pattern

```blitzbasic
; Find state machines
Function Find_StateMachines()
    ; Look for state definitions
    Grep("Const STATE_", "*.bb")

    ; Look for state switches
    Grep("Select.*State", "*.bb")
    Grep("Switch.*State", "*.bb")

    ; Look for state updates
    Grep("Function.*State.*Update", "*.bb")
End Function
```

### Type Pattern

```blitzbasic
; Find type definitions
Function Find_TypeDefinitions()
    Grep("^Type ", "*.bb")

    ; List all Type fields
    ForEach file$ in "*.bb"
        Grep("^Type ", file$)
        Grep("^    Field ", file$)  ; With indentation
    Next
End Function
```

### Event Pattern

```blitzbasic
; Find event systems
Function Find_EventSystems()
    ; Event definitions
    Grep("Const EVENT_", "*.bb")

    ; Event handlers
    Grep("Function.*Event.*Handler", "*.bb")

    ; Event triggers
    Grep("TriggerEvent", "*.bb")
    Grep("RaiseEvent", "*.bb")
End Function
```

## Quick Navigation

### SCPB Specific

```blitzbasic
; NPC types
LocateFile("NPCs.bb")

; Game events
LocateFile("UpdateEvents.bb")

; Main loop
LocateFile("Main.bb")

; Map system
LocateFile("MapSystem.bb")

; Save/load
LocateFile("Save.bb")

; Menu
LocateFile("Menu.bb")

; Items
LocateFile("Items.bb")

; Configuration
LocateFile("Data/rooms.ini")
LocateFile("Data/events.ini")
```

### All Purposes

```blitzbasic
; Find by content
Grep("keyword", "*.bb")

; Find by name
glob("**/*keyword*")

; Find recent files
ListFilesByDate("*.bb", 10)

; Find largest files
ListFilesBySize("*.bb", 10)
```

## Documentation Generation

```blitzbasic
Function Generate_CodebaseDoc()
    ; Create documentation file
    file = WriteFile("CODEBASE_DOC.md")

    WriteLine file, "# Codebase Documentation"
    WriteLine file, ""
    WriteLine file, "Generated: " + Date()
    WriteLine file, ""

    ; File structure
    WriteLine file, "## File Structure"
    WriteLine file, ListTopLevelDirectories()

    ; Largest files
    WriteLine file, "## Largest Files (Most Complex)"
    GetLargestFiles(20)
    ForEach f in results
        WriteLine file, "- " + f + " (" + FileSize(f) + " bytes)"
    Next

    ; System breakdown
    WriteLine file, "## Systems"
    WriteLine file, "### NPCs"
    Summarize_File("NPCs.bb")
    WriteLine file, "### Game Events"
    Summarize_File("UpdateEvents.bb")

    CloseFile(file)
    Print "Documentation generated: CODEBASE_DOC.md"
End Function
```

## Quick Reference

| Goal | Command |
|------|---------|
| Find function | `Grep("Function name", "*.bb")` |
| Find type | `Grep("^Type name", "*.bb")` |
| Find calls to | `Grep("functionName(", "*.bb")` |
| Find uses of var | `Grep("variableName", "*.bb")` |
| List file contents | `Grep("^Function ", file$)` |
| Find includes | `Grep("#Include", file$)` |
| Map system | `Grep("Const STATE_", "*.bb")` |
| Find main | `glob("**/main*")` |
